"title": "5198: weeping",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5198: weeping",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The physical act of shedding tears as the result of sadness or joy or in recognition of sin.</p>\n<h2>Weeping in personal grief</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen23:2\">GEN 23:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:3\">PSA 42:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev5:4\">REV 5:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:38\">GEN 27:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:35\">GEN 37:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:37\">JDG 11:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:9\">RUT 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:8\">1SA 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:41\">1SA 20:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:16\">2SA 3:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam13:19\">2SA 13:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam15:30\">2SA 15:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam18:33\">2SA 18:33</a> <em>David weeps for Absalom</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs8:11\">2KI 8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs13:14\">2KI 13:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:3\">2KI 20:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:16\">JOB 16:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job16:20\">JOB 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:12\">PSA 39:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps56:8\">PSA 56:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps102:9\">PSA 102:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:33\">JHN 11:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:11\">JHN 20:11</a></p>\n<h2>Weeping in shared grief</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut34:8\">DEU 34:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps137:1\">PSA 137:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:1\">NUM 14:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam11:4-1Sam11:5\">1SA 11:4–11:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam20:41\">1SA 20:41</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam30:4\">1SA 30:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:12\">2SA 1:12</a> <em>David and his men mourn for Saul and Jonathan</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam1:24\">2SA 1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:34\">2SA 3:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:12\">JOB 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps80:4-Ps80:5\">PSA 80:4–80:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa15:2-Isa15:3\">ISA 15:2–15:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:7\">ISA 33:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark5:38\">MRK 5:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:13\">ACT 21:13</a></p>\n<h2>Weeping in personal remorse over failure and sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:75\">MAT 26:75</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:72\">MRK 14:72</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:62\">LUK 22:62</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:33\">1SA 2:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:38\">LUK 7:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:17\">HEB 12:17</a></p>\n<h2>Weeping in group response to sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:9\">NEH 8:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:21\">JER 3:21</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:1\">JAS 5:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num25:6\">NUM 25:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:45\">DEU 1:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg20:26\">JDG 20:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg21:2\">JDG 21:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra3:12-Ezra3:13\">EZR 3:12–3:13</a> <em>the people's response to the rebuilding of the temple</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa22:12-Isa22:13\">ISA 22:12–22:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer25:34\">JER 25:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:9\">JER 31:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer50:4\">JER 50:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:2\">LAM 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:18\">LAM 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel2:12\">JOL 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos5:16-Amos5:17\">AMO 5:16–5:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos8:10\">AMO 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:10-Zech12:11\">ZEC 12:10–12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:12\">MAT 8:12</a></p>\n<h2>Weeping in response to others' sin and judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:136\">PSA 119:136</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:17\">JER 13:17</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor2:4\">2CO 2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra10:1\">EZR 10:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:4\">NEH 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:9\">ISA 16:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:1\">JER 9:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:17\">JER 14:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:10\">JER 22:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam1:16\">LAM 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:48\">LAM 3:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek27:31\">EZK 27:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic1:8\">MIC 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:41\">LUK 19:41</a> <em>Jesus Christ weeps over Jerusalem</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:28\">LUK 23:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:31\">ACT 20:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:18\">PHP 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:15-Rev18:16\">REV 18:15–18:16</a></p>\n<h2>Divine weeping</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:9\">ISA 16:9</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's weeping</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:35\">JHN 11:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:7\">HEB 5:7</a></p>\n<h2>Weeping for joy</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:11\">GEN 29:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen42:24\">GEN 42:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen45:14-Gen45:15\">GEN 45:14–45:15</a></p>\n<h2>False weeping</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:13\">MAL 2:13</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Comfort promised to those who weep</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps126:5-Ps126:6\">PSA 126:5–126:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:4\">REV 21:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps30:5\">PSA 30:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps116:8\">PSA 116:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:8\">ISA 25:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:19\">ISA 30:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:19\">ISA 65:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:16\">JER 31:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:21\">LUK 6:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:20\">JHN 16:20</a></p>",
